adicata]]'' <small>Hook.f.</small> *''[[Brachyscome rara]]'' <small>G.L.R.Davis</small> *''[[Brachyscome readeri]]'' <small>G.L.R.Davis</small> &ndash; southern daisy<ref name=NSW/> *''[[Brachyscome rigidula]]'' <small>(DC.) G.L.R.Davis</small> &ndash; hairy cut-leaf daisy, cut-leaf daisy<ref name=NSW/> *''[[Brachyscome riparia]]'' <small>G.L.R.Davis</small> *''[[Brachyscome scapigera]]'' <small> (Sieber ex Spreng.) DC.</small> &ndash; tufted daisy<ref name=NSW/> *''[[Brachyscome segmentosa]]'' <small>C.Moore & F.Muell.</small> &ndash; Lord Howe Island daisy<ref name=NSW/> *''[[Brachyscome sieberi]]'' <small>DC.</small> *''[[Brachyscome smithwhitei]]'' <small>P.S.Short & Watan.</small> *''[[Brachyscome spathulata]]'' <small>Gaudich.</small> *''[[Brachyscome stolonifera]]'' <small>G.L.R.Davis</small> *''[[Brachyscome stuartii]]'' <small>Benth.</small> *''[[Brachyscome tatei]]'' <small>J.M.Black</small> *''[[Brachyscome tenuiscapa]]'' <small>Hook.f.</small> *''[[Brachyscome tesquorum]]'' <small>J.M.Black</small> *''[[Brachyscome tetrapterocarpa]]'' <small>G.L.R.Davis</small> *''[[Brachyscome trachycarpa]]'' <small>F.Muell.</small> &ndash; inland daisy, smooth daisy<ref name=NSW/> *''[[Brachyscome uliginosa]]'' <small>G.L.R.Davis</small> *''[[Brachyscome whitei]]'' <small>G.L.R.Davis</small> &ndash; spreading daisy<ref name=NSW/> *''[[Brachyscome xanthocarpa]]'' <small>D.A.Cooke</small>
